## üîß CONFIGURATION

### Required:
```env
# MongoDB (start with: mongod)
MONGO_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/techcare

# For Google Maps (Mobile/PC Repair pages)
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_key_here
```

### Optional:
```env
# Currency API (has fallback)
VITE_CURRENCY_API_KEY=your_key

# Email (for notifications)
SMTP_USER=your_email
SMTP_PASS=your_password
```

